; Test payee-rewrite directive (line 558 of textual_directives.cc)
; Exercise the payee_rewrite_mappings flow
; The rewrite applies at report time; each posting is in a separate xact

payee-rewrite Groceries  Grocery Store

2024/01/01 Groceries
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Grocery Store         Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
24-Jan-01 Grocery Store         Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
end test
